Russia’s RTS Stock-Index Futures Advance at Start of Trading

-- B y   H a l i a   P a v l i v a
-- 
2011-03-14T16:25:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/russia-s-rts-stock-index-futures-advance-at-start-of-trading.html
  Russia ’s RTS stock-index futures
gained at the start of trading.  Futures on the dollar-denominated index expiring in March
added 0.1 percent to 192,195 at 11:21 a.m. in  New York .  Contracts on OAO Sberbank, Russia’s largest lender,
increased 0.9 percent, while futures on OAO Gazprom, the
natural-gas export monopoly, fell 0.2 percent. Contracts on OAO
Lukoil, the country’s second-biggest oil producer, rose 0.2
percent. The Market Vectors Russia ETF, a U.S.-traded fund that
holds Russian shares, slid 0.1 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Halia Pavliva in New York at 
 hpavliva@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
